This directory contains the reference implementation of the SnuPL/1 scanner.

To use this scanner instead of your own, perform the following steps:

1. create a directory 'lib' under 'snuplc'
   $ mkdir ../snuplc/lib

2. copy scanner.o to the newly created directory
   $ cp scanner.o ../snuplc/lib/

3. copy scanner.h to the source directory
   $ cp scanner.h ../snuplc/src/

4. replace the Makefile in snuplc/ with the one here
   $ cp Makefile ../snuplc/


